<main>
  <section class="p-0">
    <%= render "home/carrossel" %>
  </section>
  <section class="orar-lotes-section py-5">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="text-center mb-5">
        <p class="orar-section-kicker mb-2">Inscrições</p>
        <h1 class="display-5 fw-semibold mb-2">Escolha seu lote</h1>
        <p class="text-secondary mb-0">Garanta sua vaga no ORAR 2026 com o lote disponível no momento da inscrição.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="row justify-content-center">
        <div class="col-12 col-lg-10">
          <article class="card orar-lote-card orar-lote-card--single h-100">
            <div class="card-body p-4 p-md-5 d-flex flex-column flex-md-row align-items-center justify-content-between gap-4">
              <div class="text-center text-md-start">
                <p class="orar-lote-etiqueta mb-3">Lote único</p>
                <p class="orar-lote-descricao mb-0">Período de inscrição: 29/04 - 30/05.</p>
              </div>

              <div class="orar-lote-preco mb-0">
                <span class="orar-lote-moeda">R$</span>
                <span class="orar-lote-valor">65,00</span>
              </div>

              <%= link_to "Link de pagamento", inscricoes_path, class: "btn orar-lote-botao orar-lote-botao--single" %>
            </div>
          </article>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-5">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="text-center mb-4">
        <h2 class="fw-bold mb-2">Fotos do último ORAR</h2>
      </div>

      <% galeria_imagens = [
        ["ulisses", "Ulisses"],
        ["candeias", "Candeias"],
        ["setimus", "Setimus"],
        ["forjados", "Forjados"],
        ["volei", "Volei"],
        ["eldorado", "Eldorado"]
      ] %>

      <div class="row g-4">
        <% galeria_imagens.each do |image, alt_text| %>
          <div class="col-12 col-sm-6 col-lg-4">
            <div class="orar-galeria-card shadow-sm rounded-3">
              <%= responsive_asset_picture(
                "#{image}-1200.webp",
                alt: alt_text,
                sizes: "(min-width: 992px) 33vw, (min-width: 576px) 50vw, 100vw",
                width: 1200,
                height: 800,
                srcset: [["#{image}-480.webp", "480w"], ["#{image}-800.webp", "800w"], ["#{image}-1200.webp", "1200w"]],
                picture_class: "orar-galeria-midia",
                img_class: "orar-galeria-imagem",
                aspect_ratio: "4 / 3"
              ) %>
            </div>
          </div>
        <% end %>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="container mt-5">
      <h2 class="d-flex align-items-center justify-content-center gap-2 mb-4">
        <span aria-hidden="true">
          <i class="bi bi-question-circle-fill"></i>
        </span>
        Perguntas Frequentes
      </h2>

      <div class="row g-4 justify-content-center orar-faq-grid">
        <div class="col-12 col-lg-6">
          <div class="card shadow-sm faq-card" onclick="toggleAnswer(this)">
            <div class="card-body">
              <div class="row align-items-center">
                <div class="col-10">
                  <h5 class="fw-bold text-secondary mb-0">1. O que e o ORAR?</h5>
                </div>
                <div class="col-2 text-end">
                  <i class="bi bi-plus-lg text-secondary" aria-hidden="true"></i>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="faq-answer">
                <p class="text-secondary mt-3 mb-0">
                  A olimpíada regional Adventista de Rôndonia, <strong>ORAR</strong>, é uma iniciativa do Ministério Jovem para promover evolução física, mental e espiritual dos jovens. O objetivo e proporcionar um ambiente saudável e estimulante para o desenvolvimento integral dos participantes, fortalecendo a integração entre os distritos.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="col-12 col-lg-6">
          <div class="card shadow-sm faq-card" onclick="toggleAnswer(this)">
            <div class="card-body">
              <div class="row align-items-center">
                <div class="col-10">
                  <h5 class="fw-bold text-secondary mb-0">2. Quem pode participar?</h5>
                </div>
                <div class="col-2 text-end">
                  <i class="bi bi-plus-lg text-secondary" aria-hidden="true"></i>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="faq-answer">
                <ul class="text-secondary mt-3 mb-0">
                  <li>Todos aqueles que frequentam regularmente uma sociedade jovem.</li>
                </ul>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="col-12 col-lg-6">
          <div class="card shadow-sm faq-card" onclick="toggleAnswer(this)">
            <div class="card-body">
              <div class="row align-items-center">
                <div class="col-10">
                  <h5 class="fw-bold text-secondary mb-0">3. Quando e onde vai ser o ORAR 2026?</h5>
                </div>
                <div class="col-2 text-end">
                  <i class="bi bi-plus-lg text-secondary" aria-hidden="true"></i>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="faq-answer">
                <ul class="text-secondary mt-3 mb-0">
                  <li>O ORAR 2026 será realizado na Igreja Adventista do Setímo dia central de Porto Velho e também no Colégio Adventista de Porto Velho, no período de 05 de junho a 07 de junho de 2026.</li>
                </ul>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <script>
      function toggleAnswer(card) {
        const answer = card.querySelector(".faq-answer");
        const icon = card.querySelector("i");

        answer.classList.toggle("active");

        if (answer.classList.contains("active")) {
          icon.classList.remove("bi-plus-lg");
          icon.classList.add("bi-dash-lg");
        } else {
          icon.classList.remove("bi-dash-lg");
          icon.classList.add("bi-plus-lg");
        }
      }
    </script>

    <style>
      .orar-lotes-section {
        background:
          radial-gradient(circle at top, rgba(217, 230, 245, 0.7), transparent 48%),
          linear-gradient(180deg, #f8fbff 0%, #ffffff 100%);
      }

      .orar-section-kicker {
        color: #2a5788;
        font-family: "Montserrat", sans-serif;
        font-size: 0.85rem;
        font-weight: 700;
        letter-spacing: 0.16em;
        text-transform: uppercase;
      }

      .orar-lote-card {
        border: 1px solid rgba(22, 58, 99, 0.08);
        border-radius: 24px;
        box-shadow: 0 18px 40px rgba(28, 54, 84, 0.08);
        transition: transform 0.25s ease, box-shadow 0.25s ease;
      }

      .orar-lote-card:hover {
        box-shadow: 0 22px 48px rgba(28, 54, 84, 0.14);
        transform: translateY(-4px);
      }

      .orar-lote-card--featured {
        background: linear-gradient(160deg, #163a63 0%, #2a5788 100%);
        border-color: rgba(22, 58, 99, 0.16);
        color: #f3f0e6;
      }

      .orar-lote-card--single {
        background:
          linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(243, 240, 230, 0.12), rgba(243, 240, 230, 0) 34%),
          linear-gradient(135deg, #163a63 0%, #2a5788 48%, #5e86b5 100%);
        border-color: rgba(22, 58, 99, 0.18);
        color: #f3f0e6;
        min-height: 240px;
      }

      .orar-lote-card--single .orar-lote-descricao {
        color: rgba(243, 240, 230, 0.82);
      }

      .orar-lote-card--single .orar-lote-moeda {
        color: #f3f0e6;
      }

      .orar-lote-badge {
        background: rgba(243, 240, 230, 0.14);
        border: 1px solid rgba(243, 240, 230, 0.28);
        border-radius: 999px;
        color: inherit;
        font-family: "Montserrat", sans-serif;
        font-size: 0.72rem;
        font-weight: 700;
        letter-spacing: 0.12em;
        padding: 0.45rem 0.9rem;
        text-transform: uppercase;
      }

      .orar-lote-etiqueta {
        color: inherit;
        font-family: "Montserrat", sans-serif;
        font-size: 1.1rem;
        font-weight: 700;
        letter-spacing: 0.08em;
        text-transform: uppercase;
      }

      .orar-lote-preco {
        align-items: baseline;
        display: flex;
        gap: 0.35rem;
        justify-content: center;
      }

      .orar-lote-moeda {
        color: #2a5788;
        font-family: "Montserrat", sans-serif;
        font-size: 1.4rem;
        font-weight: 700;
      }

      .orar-lote-card--featured .orar-lote-moeda {
        color: #f3f0e6;
      }

      .orar-lote-valor {
        color: inherit;
        font-family: "Montserrat", sans-serif;
        font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 4vw, 3.5rem);
        font-weight: 700;
        line-height: 1;
      }

      .orar-lote-descricao {
        font-size: 0.98rem;
        line-height: 1.6;
      }

      .orar-lote-card--featured .orar-lote-descricao {
        color: rgba(243, 240, 230, 0.82) !important;
      }

      .orar-lote-botao {
        background: transparent;
        border: 1px solid #2a5788;
        border-radius: 999px;
        color: #2a5788;
        font-family: "Montserrat", sans-serif;
        font-size: 0.9rem;
        font-weight: 700;
        letter-spacing: 0.08em;
        padding: 0.95rem 1.5rem;
        text-transform: uppercase;
      }

      .orar-lote-botao:hover {
        background: #2a5788;
        color: #ffffff;
      }

      .orar-lote-botao--featured {
        background: #f3f0e6;
        border-color: #f3f0e6;
        color: #163a63;
      }

      .orar-lote-botao--featured:hover {
        background: transparent;
        color: #f3f0e6;
      }

      .orar-lote-botao--single {
        background: #f3f0e6;
        border-color: #f3f0e6;
        color: #163a63;
      }

      .orar-lote-botao--single:hover {
        background: transparent;
        color: #f3f0e6;
      }

      .orar-galeria-card {
        overflow: hidden;
        background: #f8f9fa;
      }

      .orar-galeria-midia {
        display: block;
        width: 100%;
      }

      .orar-galeria-imagem {
        width: 100%;
        height: 100%;
        object-fit: cover;
        object-position: center;
      }

      .faq-card {
        cursor: pointer;
        border: none;
        border-radius: 10px;
      }

      .faq-card:hover {
        box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
      }

      .faq-answer {
        max-height: 0;
        overflow: hidden;
        transition: max-height 0.3s ease-out;
      }

      .faq-answer.active {
        max-height: 220px;
      }

      @media (max-width: 768px) {
        .orar-lotes-section .display-5 {
          font-size: 2.2rem;
        }

        .orar-lote-card--single {
          min-height: auto;
        }

        .orar-lote-card--single .card-body {
          align-items: stretch !important;
          text-align: center;
        }

        .orar-lote-card--single .orar-lote-preco {
          width: 100%;
        }

        .orar-lote-botao--single {
          width: 100%;
        }

        .faq-card h5 {
          font-size: 1rem;
        }

        .faq-card i {
          font-size: 1.2rem;
        }
      }
    </style>
  </section>
</main>
